Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:09.99,Warning,,0,0,0,,{\org(0,0)\fscx0\fscy0\clip(0,0,0,0)}Your media player does not support the subtitle format used in this episode. Subtitles will likely not function properly. Please use one of the recommended video players, preferably mpv: https://mpv.io
